\begin_layout Section
习题
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
1.
 pf.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
用归纳法, 当点数
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)=1$
\end_inset

时, 问题显然成立.
 假设
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)=n$
\end_inset

时命题成立.
 现在考虑
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)=n+1$
\end_inset

的情况.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

是树, 所以必然存在顶点的度数为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

, 否则任取一点
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

染色, 并从
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

发出的线中任取一条边
\begin_inset Formula $e_{1}$
\end_inset

, 它连接的顶点记为
\begin_inset Formula $v_{2}$
\end_inset

, 并对
\begin_inset Formula $v_{2}$
\end_inset

染色, 如果
\begin_inset Formula $v_{2}$
\end_inset

的度至少是
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

, 则除了
\begin_inset Formula $e_{1}$
\end_inset

外还有另一条边
\begin_inset Formula $e_{2}$
\end_inset

, 如此下去, 由于图的顶点数有限, 这种取法必然在有限步内到达一个已经被染色的顶点
\begin_inset Formula $v_{i}$
\end_inset

, 这与树是无环图矛盾.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
取
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

的度数为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

的顶点
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

, 从树中去掉这个顶点以及唯一与其相连接的边后形成图
\begin_inset Formula $T'$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $v(T')=n$
\end_inset

, 由归纳假设
\begin_inset Formula $v(T')-e(T')=1$
\end_inset

, 而
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)=v(T')+1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $e(T)=e(T')+1$
\end_inset

.
 即得
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)-e(T)=1$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
1.
 pf2
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
可以对边数使用归纳法, 从树
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

中去掉一条边, 则将原来的树分成两个子树
\begin_inset Formula $T_{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{2}$
\end_inset

, 从而
\begin_inset Formula $v(T)=v(T_{1})+v(T_{2})$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $e(T)=e(T_{1})+e(T_{2})+1$
\end_inset

, 所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v(T)-e(T)=v(T_{1})+v(T_{2})-e(T_{1})-e(T_{2})-1=1.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
2.
 pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
本题条件中的图精确来说是指连通图.
 由第1题的结论, 已经证明了当
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

是树时, 有
\begin_inset Formula $v(\Gamma)-e(\Gamma)=1$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于任何连通图
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

都包含一个树
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

, 而
\begin_inset Formula $v(\Gamma)=v(T)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $e(\Gamma)\ge e(T)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v(\Gamma)-e(\Gamma)\le v(T)-e(T)=1.
\]

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $v(\Gamma)-e(\Gamma)=1$
\end_inset

时, 必然有一个点的度数是
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

, 否则由于每条边有两个顶点, 当统计边的总数时同时统计连接的两个点, 则统计出的点数(重复计数统计)恰好是边数的两倍, 也恰好是所有顶点的度数之和,
 即如果记
\begin_inset Formula $d(v)$
\end_inset

为顶点
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

的度数, 有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sum d(v_{i})=2e(\Gamma)\ge2v(\Gamma)=2e(\Gamma)+2,
\]

\end_inset

矛盾.
 如果点
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

的度数是
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

, 则可从
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

中除去这个点和它发出的边, 然后根据归纳法可得
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

是一棵树.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
3.
 pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
题目中的图
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

是连通图.
 可以考虑树的生长过程, 任取一点
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

, 设
\begin_inset Formula $A=\left\{ v_{1}\right\} $
\end_inset

.
 由于图是连通图, 且
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

有出度.
 所以可以将
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

中与
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}$
\end_inset

距离是
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

的所有顶点放入
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中, 并将连接到
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中点的边染色.
 由于
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

的连通性, 从
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

中又可找到与
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

距离是
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

的顶点, 将其放入
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中, 并将连接到
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中的边中任取一条染色.
 如此继续下去直到
\begin_inset Formula $\Gamma$
\end_inset

中的所有顶点都放入
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

中, 则染色的边与顶点
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

形成一棵树.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
6.
 pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于一条边由两个面所共用, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $fp=2e$
\end_inset

.
 由于一个顶点发出
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

条边, 一条边由两个顶点组成, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $vq=2e$
\end_inset

即得.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
8.pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $v-e+f=-2$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
10.pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{2}+\frac{1}{\pi}\arctan x:\RR\to(0,1)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Note Note
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
