\begin_layout Section
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "sec:3.4"

\end_inset

乘积空间
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

为拓扑空间, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{B}$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $X\times Y$
\end_inset

内形如
\begin_inset Formula $U\times V$
\end_inset

的子集族, 其中
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

中开集, 
\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

中开集, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\cup\mathscr{B}=X\times Y$
\end_inset

, 且
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{B}$
\end_inset

中任意两个成员的交集仍然属于
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{B}$
\end_inset

.
 则称
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{B}$
\end_inset

构成
\begin_inset Formula $X\times Y$
\end_inset

上的一组拓扑基
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
拓扑基
\end_layout

\end_inset

, 这个拓扑叫做乘积拓扑
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
乘积拓扑
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 集合
\begin_inset Formula $X\times Y$
\end_inset

连通乘积拓扑一起称为乘积空间
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
乘积空间
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
按照
\begin_inset Formula $p_{1}(x,y)=x$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{2}(x,y)=y$
\end_inset

定义的映射
\begin_inset Formula $p_{1}:X\times Y\to X$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{2}:X\times Y\to Y$
\end_inset

叫做投影
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
投影
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.12"

\end_inset

 若
\begin_inset Formula $X\times Y$
\end_inset

有乘积拓扑, 则投影是连续开映射.
 乘积拓扑是
\begin_inset Formula $X\times Y$
\end_inset

上使两个投影都连续的最小拓扑.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
连续用定义来证; 开映射在拓扑基上来证; 乘积拓扑的最小性由``任何使投影连续的拓扑必然包含乘积拓扑的拓扑基''来证.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.13"

\end_inset

 映射
\begin_inset Formula $f:Z\to X\times Y$
\end_inset

连续, 当且仅当两个复合映射
\begin_inset Formula $p_{1}f:Z\to X$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{2}f:Z\to Y$
\end_inset

连续.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
必要性: 用连续函数的复合(定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:2.7"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

); 充分性用
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f^{-1}\left(U\times V\right)=(p_{1}f)^{-1}(U)\cap(p_{2}f)^{-1}(V).
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.14"

\end_inset

 乘积空间
\begin_inset Formula $X\times Y$
\end_inset

为Hausdorff空间, 当且仅当
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

为Hausdorff空间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.15"

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $X\times Y$
\end_inset

紧致, 当且仅当
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

都紧致.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
充分性的证明依赖下面的引理.
 必要性用定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.12"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

和
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.4-1"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

即可.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Lemma
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "lem:3.16"

\end_inset

 设
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

为拓扑空间, 设
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{B}$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的一组拓扑基, 则
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

紧致, 当且仅当, 由
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{B}$
\end_inset

中元素组成的
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的开覆盖有有限子覆盖.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Argument 1
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.1"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.1-1"

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $E^{n}$
\end_inset

的子集为紧致集, 当且仅当它是有界闭的.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
必要性部分证明在定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.9"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
 充分性用定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.15"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

, Heine-Borel定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.3-1"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

和定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.5-1"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
定义无穷多个空间的乘积空间, 证明任意多个紧致空间的乘积是紧致空间, 称为Tychonoff定理; 它等价于选择公理.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
连通性
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "def:3.17"

\end_inset

 拓扑空间
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

是连通
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
连通
\end_layout

\end_inset

的, 如果当它分解为两个非空子集的并集
\begin_inset Formula $A\cup B$
\end_inset

时, 有
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{A}\cap B\ne\varnothing$
\end_inset

, 或
\begin_inset Formula $A\cap\overline{B}\ne\varnothing$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.18"

\end_inset

 实数轴是连通空间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
按定义证明, 用极限点的概念和确界原理.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
拓扑空间的子集叫做连通子集
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
连通子集
\end_layout

\end_inset

, 如果给以诱导拓扑时, 它是一个连通空间.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
称实数轴的子集
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

是一个区间
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
区间
\end_layout

\end_inset

, 如果对于任意两个不同的点
\begin_inset Formula $a,b\in X$
\end_inset

, (
\begin_inset Formula $a<b$
\end_inset

), 有
\begin_inset Formula $\forall c\in(a,b)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $c\in X$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.19"

\end_inset

 实数轴上的非空子集连通, 当且仅当它是一个区间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
充分性, 用定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.18"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
 必要性, 用反证法和连通性定义构造矛盾.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.20"

\end_inset

 对于空间
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

, 以下条件相互等价:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
(a).
 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

连通;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
(b).
 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

内同时为开集与闭集的子集只有
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

与空集;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
(c).
 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

不能表示成两个不交非空开集之并;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
(d).
 不存在从
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

到一个多于一点的离散拓扑空间的连续满射.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.21"

\end_inset

 连通空间的连续像是连通空间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
证明使用定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.20"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

的(b).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Corollary
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "cor:3.22"

\end_inset

 若
\begin_inset Formula $h:X\to Y$
\end_inset

是同胚, 则
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

连通, 当且仅当
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

连通.
 即连通性是空间的拓扑性质.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.21"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

的推论.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.23"

\end_inset

 设
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

是拓扑空间, 
\begin_inset Formula $Z$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的子集.
 若
\begin_inset Formula $Z$
\end_inset

连通, 且在
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

内稠密, 则
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

连通.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
证明使用定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.20"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Corollary
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "cor:3.24"

\end_inset

 若
\begin_inset Formula $Z$
\end_inset

是拓扑空间
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的连通子集, 且若
\begin_inset Formula $Z\subseteq Y\subseteq\overline{Z}$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

连通.
 特别地, 
\begin_inset Formula $Z$
\end_inset

的闭包
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{Z}$
\end_inset

连通.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
用定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.23"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

是空间
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的子集, 且若
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{A}\cap\overline{B}=\varnothing$
\end_inset

, 则称
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

内是相互分离的.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.25"

\end_inset

 设
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{F}$
\end_inset

是空间
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

的一族子集, 它们的并集是整个
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

.
 若
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{F}$
\end_inset

的每个成员是连通的, 且
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{F}$
\end_inset

的任意两个成员在
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

内都不是互相分离的, 则
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

连通.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
证明用定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
