\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.26"

\end_inset

 若
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

是连通空间, 则乘积空间
\begin_inset Formula $X\times Y$
\end_inset

是连通的.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
用定理
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:3.25"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若一个空间不是连通的, 则它分裂为一些连通块的并集, 其中任意两个是相互分离的, 称这些连通块为连通分支.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:3.27"

\end_inset

 拓扑空间的连通分支为闭集, 不同的连通分支在空间内是相互分离的.
\end_layout

